cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.SOC, cs.DL, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the following arXiv CS sub-categories:
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks): The paper focuses on analyzing and predicting cascades on social networking websites such as Facebook and Twitter. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering): The paper may involve software engineering techniques for data collection and analysis. 
- cs.SOC (Computational Social Science): The paper is related to the study of social phenomena using computational methods. 
- cs.DL (Digital Libraries): The paper may involve techniques for managing and analyzing large amounts of data from social networking websites. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The paper may involve techniques for analyzing and predicting the spread of information on social networking websites.
